Package: sapiaR
Title: Download and plot maps from the Southern African Plant Invaders Atlas (SAPIA)
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person(given = "Guy Frederick",
           family = "Sutton",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "g.sutton@ru.ac.za")
Description: This package allows users to download data and analyse data from the Southern African Plant Invaders Atlas (SAPIA). 
             The primary function is to plot the characteristic distribution maps obtained from SAPIA, and calculate basic summary statistics. 
Depends: R (>= 2.10)
Imports: 
    dplyr,
    magrittr,
    purrr,
    tidyr,
    ggplot2,
    knitr,
    rlang,
    cowplot
License: CC0
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.1.1
